IMPORTANT — Licensing of released model weights

This MIT license covers the SOURCE CODE in this repository only.

The VintageVoice model weights published on Hugging Face are a fine-tune of
F5-TTS (SWivid/F5-TTS), whose pretrained weights are distributed under the
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 (CC-BY-NC-4.0) license. Because
our fine-tune is a mathematical derivative of those base weights, the released
VintageVoice model weights inherit CC-BY-NC-4.0. That means:

  * The weights may be used, modified, and redistributed for non-commercial
    purposes with attribution.
  * Commercial use of the weights requires a separate arrangement with the
    upstream F5-TTS authors; see https://huggingface.co/SWivid/F5-TTS .

The training data is 100% public domain, sourced from Archive.org and similar
archives of pre-1955 recordings. The data itself carries no restrictions.

Summary:
  Code ............... MIT (this file)
  Model weights ...... CC-BY-NC-4.0 (inherited from F5-TTS base)
  Training data ...... Public domain
